quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"Simoore, Min njippinii nde Min farlii nde, Min njippini e ndeer mayre aayeeje …ďanngu…óe mbelejo'o onon on mbaajitoto."
  24,2,"Debbo jinoowo on e gorko jinoowo on foccee gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe paatawol(looci) teemedere, wota njurmeende ma…ď…ďe nanngu on e fii Diina Alla ka, si tawii on laatike ho…óon ngooŇč…óini Alla e √Ďalaande Laakara nden. Yo seedo foccugol …ďe ngol jamaa immorde e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  24,3,"Gorko jinoowo on o resataa si wonaa debbo jonoowo maa…óum cirkoowo, debbo jinoowo on resata mo si wonaa gorko jinoowo ma cirkoowo, …óum harminaama e dow gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen."
  24,4,"E …ďen …ďe no tukka rew…ďe saŇčii…ďe …ďen refti …ďe ngaddaani seedee…ďe nayo, piyee …ďe paatawol(lo'oci) cappan…óe jeetati. Wota on nja…ďan …ďe ceedagol poomaa. ∆Āen …óon, ko kam…ďe ngoni Faasiqii…ďe …ďen."
  24,5,"Si wonaa …ďen tuubu…ďe …ďaawo …óuum …ďe mo∆ī∆īini. Pellet, Alla ko O cuhroowo jurmetee…óo."
  24,6,"E …ďeen …ďe no tukka sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen hara laatanaaki …ďe seedee…ďe si wonaa wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko yo go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla pellet, kako ko e googu…ďe …ďen o jeyaa."
  24,7,"Jowa…ďun …óum, won'dema yo kuddi Alla wonu e dow makko si o laatike jeyaa…óo e fenoo…ďe …ďeen."
  24,8,"∆Āe ndu√Īira e [sonnaajo on] lepte …óen, nde o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet [gorko on] ko e fenoo…ďe …ďen o jeyaa."
  24,9,"Jowa…ďum …óum, ko nde Alla tikkata e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike ko e gooŇču…ďe …ďen o jeyaa."
  24,10,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden, e wonan'dema Alla ko O ja…ďoowo tuubuubuye √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  24,11,"Pellet, …ďeen addu…ďe penaale …óen ko …ďe jamaa jeyaa…óo e moo…óon, wota on cikku …óum ko bone mo'on; ko woni …óum ko mo∆ī∆īere mo'on. No woodani kala ne…ó…óo immorde e ma…ď…ďe ko o faggitii kon e bakkaat, on fawtii…óo [bakkaat on] immorde e ma…ď…ďe, no woodani mo Lepte maw…óe."
  24,12,"Ko ha…óno oo tuma nde nan…óon …óum, wor…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen e rew…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen …ďe njananee ka wonkiiji ma…ď…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi, …ďe mbi'a: ""∆äum ko penaale …ďanngu…óe nii""."
  24,13,"Ko ha…óno ko nde …ďe ngaddata e …óum seedee…ďe nayo, si …ďe ngaddaani seedee…ďe …ďen; haray …ďeen …óon, to Alla ko kam…ďe ngoni fenoo…ďe …ďen."
  24,14,"Sinndo wonaano …ďural Alla ngal e yurmeende makko nden e dow moo…óon e aduna e yo La'akara Lepte maw…óe meematno on fii kon ko ukki…óon e muu…óum."
  24,15,"Tuma nde werlorayno…óon …óum …óenm…óe moo…óon, wowliron kunndu…óe moo…óon kon ko ganndal alana on e muu…óum sikkon …óum kadi ko newii…óum, hara non …óum ko mawnu…óom ka Alla."
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nan…óon nde, mbi'on: ""Haanaa min nde min wowlata e dum, Senayee woodanii ma, …óum ko fenaande mawnde nii""."
  24,17,"Alla no waajaade on fii wota on fillo sugu [ndee fenaande] poomaa, si tawii on laatike gooŇč…óin…ďe."
  24,18,"Alla no …ďannginannde on Aayeeje …óen Alla ko O gandu…óo √Īee√Ī…óo."
  24,19,"Pellet, …ďeen yi…ó…ďe yo bone …óen sa'ako e [hoore] …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe; no woodani …ďe Lepte muus…óe ka aduna e ka Laakara. Alla no Anndi, onon on nganndah."
  24,20,"Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende makko nden e tawde pellet, Alla ko o Newii…óo jurmotoo…óo o."
  24,21,"Eey mon …ďen gooŇč …óin…ďe, wota on mjokku …óate Seytaane …óen, kala jokku…óo …óate Seytaane …óen, pellet, o yamirat [mo] ko boni kon e ko a√Īaa kon. Sinndo wonaano ∆Āural Alla ngal e dow moo…óon e Yurmeende Makko nden; hay e gooto e moo…óon laa…ďataano poomaa, kono Alla homo la…ď…ďina on mo o muuyi. Alla ko O Nanoowo ganndu…óo."
  24,22,"Wota joomiraa…ďe …ďural ngal e yaajeende nde e moo…óon woo…óndu wonan'dema …ďe okkortaa …ďadondiraa…ďe …ďen e …ďillii…ďe …ďen e fer…ďe …ďen ka Laawol Alla, yo …ďe yaafo. Kaa on yi…óaa yo Alla yawtan on? Alla ko o jawtoowo Yurmetee…óo."
  24,23,"Pellet, …ďeen won…ďe tukkude [sonnaa…ďe] saŇčii…ďe welsindii…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe, …ďe hu…óaama ka aduna e ka Laakara no woodani …ďe Lepte maw…óe."
  24,24,"√Ďande seedoytoo e dow ma…ď…ďe …óem…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, ko …ďe laatinoo kon he…ďe ngolla."
  24,25,"Nden √Ďande Alla huu…ďinanay …ďe [njo…ďdi] Diina ma…ď…ďe Goongaha kan, …ďe ngannda pellet, Alla ko KaŇčko woni Goonga ∆Āannguka kan."
  24,26,"Rew…ďe so…ď…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe so…ď…ďe …ďen. Wor…ďe so…ď…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe so…ďu…ďe …ďen. Rew…ďe laa…ď…ďe …ďen ko fii wor…ďe laa…ď…ďe …ďen, wor…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen ko fii rew…ďe laa…ďu…ďe …ďen. ∆Āee …óoo ko hisnaa…ďe e kon ko …ďe wowlata, no woodani …ďe haforaneede e arsike teddu…óo."
  24,27,"Eey mon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe, wota on naat e cuu…ói tanaa cuu…ói mo'on …óin haa duŇčino…óon calminon e dow yim…ďe majji …ďen, ko …óum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde on. Mbelejo'o jo'o onon on mbaajitoto."
  24,28,"Si on tawaani ndeer ton go…ó…óo, wota on naat toon haa duŇčane…óon, si on mbi'aama: ""Yiltee"" yiltee, ko …óuum …ďuri laa…ďannde on. Alla non homo Anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  24,29,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde naatoton e cuu…ói …ói ko…óiraaka hara no e ndeer majji miranhoy mo'on, Alla non homo Anndi ko ngon…óon e fe√Ī√Īinde e ko ngon…óon e suu…óude."
  24,30,"Maakan wor…ďe goo…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe meeru ndaar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďe ndeena farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, ko …óuum …ďurata la…ď…ďinnde …ďe. Pellet, Alla ko o kumpitii…óo ko …ďe ngollata."
  24,31,"Maakan rew…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen yo …ďe meernu ndaar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe ndeena farjuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin, wota …ďe pe√Ī√Īin cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin si wonaa ko fee√Īi kon e mayri. Yo …ďe fawu tiggaaje ma…ď…ďe …óen ka becce ma…ď…ďe, wota …ďe fe√Ī√Īinan cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe ndin si wonaa genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen ma baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe ma baabiraa…ďe genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe ma …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, ma …ďi…ó…ďe genndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe ma musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, ma …ďi…ó…ďe musi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe, ma …ďi…ó…ďe banndiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, ma sonnaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe, maa…óum …ďen …ďe …ďe jeyiri √Īaame ma…ď…ďe ma …ďen wor…ďe jokkoo…ďe …ďe haaju mun alaa e rew…ďe, ma boobo mo ∆īellitaaki e awraaji sonnaa…ďe …ďen. Wata …ďe tappindir koy…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen fii yo Annde ko …ďe suu…ói kon immorde e cu…óaari ma…ď…ďe. Tuubee rutto…óon ka Alla on fow mo'on, ko onon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe mbelejo'o jo'o on malete."
  24,32,"Ndesinee …ďe ndesaani …ďeen e moo…óon e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen immorde e muccu…ďe moo…óon e hor…ďe moo…óon, si …ďe laatike waas…ďe Alla al…óinat …ďe immorde e ∆Āural makko ngal, Alla ko o jaac…óo ganndu…óo."
  24,33,"∆Āe ke…ďaani fehre desugol …ďeen yo …ďe cabbo haa Alla al…óinira …ďe ∆Āural makko ngal. ∆Āeen …óa…ď…ďat…ďe soottaade e …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon njeyi, coottaadede …ďe si on nganndii e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īere, njonnee …ďe immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wota on waawnu hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e fii jeeno, si …ďe faandike saŇčaade, wota on …óa…ď…ďu jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuu…óo …ďe pellet, Alla …ďaawo baawnugol …ďe ko O cuhroowo jurmitee…óo."
  24,34,"GooŇč…óii min njippinii e moo…óon aayeeje …ďanngu…óe e misal immorde e …ďeya wulinoo…ďe ko adii on e waaju wonan'de huloo…ďe [Alla] …ďen."
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni annoore kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, sifa annoore makko nde ko wano tu…ó…óere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e ndeer biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde hu…ď…ďa immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyaŇčkowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyaŇčkowal nebbam maggal …óam no …ďadoo jalbude, hay si yiite memaani …óam, annoore e hoore annoore, Alla no feewnira annoore makko nde oon mo o muuyi, Alla no piyana yim…ďe …ďen mise, Alla ko o ganndu…óo kala hu'unde."
  24,36,"E nder cuu…ói …ói Alla duŇčii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde makko jaŇčtee e ndeer majji Subunhinanee mo ndeer majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe."
  24,37,"Wor…ďe …ďe njulaaku e njeyngu maapintaa …óum ga jaŇčtagol Alla e √Īimnugol Juulde nden e tottu- gol askal on, he…ďe kuli √Ďalaande nde waylitoytoo e muu…óum …ďer…óe …óen e jii…óe …óen."
  24,38,"Fii yo Alla yo…ďoy…ďe ko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko …ďe ngollunoo kon, O …ďeydana …ďe e ∆Āural makko ngal. Alla no arsika on mo O muuyi ko Aldaa hasboore."
  24,39,"∆Āen yeddu…ďe, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen no mba'i wa merere won'nde e boowal, …óom…óaa…óo on no sikka ko nde ndiyam, haa si o arii e mayre o tawataa hay e hu'unde, o tawa Alla ka makko O huu…ďinana mo hasboore makko nden, Alla ko O jaaw…óo Hasboore."
  24,40,"Ma ko wano ni…ďe e maayo luggungo, no suddi ngo bempe∆ī∆īe no dow maggo bempe∆ī∆īe no dow majje duule, ni…ďe yoga e majje no e dow yoga, si o yaltinii junngo makko ngon o …ďadotaako ji'igol ngo. oon mo Alla wa…óanaani annoore hara o alaa annoore."
  24,41,"Enee, a yiaani wonan'dema Alla no subuhinanaade Mo …ďen won…ďe ka kammuuli e ka leydi e colli …óin kadi ko saffinii…ói? Gooto kala e …óii gooŇč…óii anndii juulde mu'um nden e subuhinaali mu'um …óin, Alla ko O ganndu…óo ko …ďe ngollata."
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii Laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, ko fa'ade ka Alla woni wa…ótinirde nden."
  24,43,"Enee, a nji'aani won'dema Alla homo sogga duulere, refti o hawtindira nde, refti o wa…óa nde fawondirnde ha…óa yi'a to…ďo ngon no yalta e ndeer mayre, ngo jippoo immorde ka kammu, immorde e pelle no e ndeer mayre marmalle homo heewtina …óe on mo o Muuyi, homo pottina …óe on mo o muuyi? Ndaneeri ma∆īe mayre no do'a na…ďde gii…óe …óen."
  24,44,"Alla homo waylita jemma on e √Īalawma on, pellet, na wonii e …óum tasakuyee wonan'de joomiraa…ďe jii…óe …ďen."
  24,45,"Ko Alla tagii kala kullel immorde e ndiyam, no e majji yaarooji reedu muu…óum, no e majji yaarooji koy…óe muu…óm no e majji kadi yaarooji [koy…óe] nayi. Alla homo Taga ko o muuyi, pellet, Alla ko kattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  24,46,"GooŇč…óii Min njippinii Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe, Alla no feewna on mo O muuyii fa'ade e Laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  24,47,"He…ďe mbia: ""Min gooŇč…óinii Alla e Nulaa…óo on, min …óoftike, refti huccita fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďaawo …óuum, …ďen wonaani gooŇč…óin…ďe""."
  24,48,"Si …ďe noddaama fa'ade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, tawa fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe …óuurnii…ďe."
  24,49,"Si tawii ko kam…ďe mari goonga ka, …ďe ngara e makko ko …ďe …óoftii…ďe."
  24,50,"Enee, ko nawnaare woni ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, kaa …ďe sikkiti, kaa …ďe hulu wota Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on too√Īu …ďe? Ko woni, …ďee ko kam…ďe woni too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol goo…óin…ďe …ďen si …ďe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on fii yo o √Īaawu hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ko nde …ďe mbi'ata: ""Min nanii men …óoftike."" ∆Āen …óon ko kam…ďe woni malaa…ďe …ďen."
  24,52,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e nulaa…óo makko on o kuli Alla o rentii [e Lepte makko …óen] haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe ngoni malaa…ďe …ďen."
  24,53,"∆Āe ngoo…óndiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje ma…ď…ďe, si a yamirii …ďe ma …ďe njaltu sanne. Maaku: ""wota on ngoo…óndu, …óoftaare no nganndaa, pellet, Alla ko kumpitii…óo ko ngolloton"""
  24,54,"Maaku: ""∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on"". Si …ďe nduŇčtiima anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko ndoonda …óo kon, si on …óoftike mo on peewat, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wonaa jottinngol …ďanngungol."
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe e moo…óon …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īi …óin o lomtinat …ďe ka leydi wano O lomtinirnoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ma O wee…ďinan …ďe diina ma…ď…ďe ka O welanaa …ďe, ma O wattitan …ďe …ďaawo kulol ma…ď…ďe ngol hoolaare, Yo …ďe ndewam wota …ďe cirkanam hay e hu'unde. Kala jeddu…óo …ďaawo …óum haray …ďen …óon ko kam…ďe woni faasiqii…ďe …ďen."
  24,56,"√Ďii…ďee e Juulde totton askal on …óofto…óon kadi nulaa…óo on, mbela jo'o on njurmete."
  24,57,"Wota a sikku …ďeen yeddu…ďe …ďe laawoto ka leydi, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde."
  24,58,"Eey mon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe, yo sakkintino e moo…óon …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, e …ďen …ďe njottaaki koy…óol immorde e moo…óon, laabi tati ko adii Juulde Peeral nden, e tuma mballinton conci moo…óon ka njollooro e ka …ďaawo Juulde gee∆īe ko awraaji moo…óon tati non. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fawaaki …ďe …ďaawo majji, jinndoo…ďe hakkunde moo…óon, yoga e moo…óon e dow yoga. Ko wano nii Alla …ďanngini- rani on aayeeje …óen Alla ko O ganndu…óo √Ďee√Īu…óo."
  24,59,"Si sukaa…ďe moo…óon njottike kellefuyee, yo …ďe cakkitinono wano duŇčinornoo non …ďen adii…ďe …ďe, ko wano nii Alla …ďannginiranta on sayeeje makko …óen, Alla ko O ganndu…óo √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  24,60,"E sonnaa…ďe jottii…ďe …ďen, …ďen …ďe njoortaaki desal bakkaatu fawaaki …ďe nde …ďe wallinta conci ma…ď…ďe …óin hara …ďe wonaa fe√Ī√Īin…ďe cu…óaari, ko nde …ďe nantotoo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďe, Alla ko O Nanoowo ganndu…óo."
  24,61,"Bakkaat fawaaki bum…óo on, bakkaatu fawaaki la∆īoowo on, bakkaat fawaaki √Īaw…óo on, fawaaki e wonkiiji moo…óon nde √Īaamoton ka cuu…ói moo…óon maa…óum ka cuu…ói baabiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói musi…ó…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói banndiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói bappiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói yaayiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óom ka cuu…ói kaawiraa…ďe moo…óon, maa…óum ka cuu…ói neeniraa…ďe moo…óon ka dewol, maa…óum …óin …ói jogi…óon cottir…óe muu…óum, maa…óum gi…óo moo…óon. Bakkaat fawaaki on nde kawtoton √Īaamon maa…óum √Īaamon ko on sertu…ďe. Si on naatay e cuu…ói salminee e dow woŇčkiiji moo…óon, salminango immorde ka Alla barkinaango laa…ďngo, ko wano nii Alla …ďannguniranta on aayeeje …óen mbelejo'o onon on kaqqilay."
  24,62,"Anndu gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen ko …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on, si …ďe laatike hi…ďe wonndi e makko e dow fiyaake moftu…óo, …ďe njahatah haa …ďe duŇčinoo e makko, pellet, …ďen …óa…ď…ďiray…ďe ma duŇčayee ko …ďen …óon woni gooŇč…óin…ďe Alla e Nulaa…óo makko on, si …ďe …óa…ď…ďirii ma duŇčayee fii yoga e fiyaake ma…ď…ďe, duŇčano on mo yi…ó…óaa [duŇčanaade] e ma…ď…ďe, imsinano…óaa …ďe ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko cuhroowo jurmetee…óo."
  24,63,"Wota on mba…ó noddugol Nulaa…óo on hakkunde moo…óon wano noddugol yoga e moo…óon yoga. GooŇč…óii Alla no Anndi …ďeen sortotoo…ďe e moo…óon e moltagol, …ďen won…ďe lunndaade yamaruyee makko on, yo …ďe rento fii wata fitina hi…ďu …ďe maa…óum Lempte mu'usu…óe he…ďa …ďe."
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla heeranii ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi gooŇč…óii homo Anndi ko ngon…óon e hoore mu'um kon, √Ďande …ďe nduttetee fa'ade ka makko p yeetoo …ďe ko …ďe ngollunoo kon. Alla ko O ganndu…óo kala hu'unde."
